---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="System"
  description="How this site is built: token architecture, theming mechanics and component docs."
>
  <h1>How this site is built</h1>
  <p class="page-placeholder">
    The meta case study: token architecture (DTCG, three tiers), OKLCH
    theming with a runtime hue, and component docs. Content follows once the
    system itself is in place.
  </p>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-placeholder {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-stack-md);
    max-width: 55ch;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }
</style>
